ive end|DE]]\n|[[Trey Flowers]]\n|[[2019 Detroit Lions season|Detroit Lions]]\n|March 14, 2019<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.detroitlions.com/news/lions-sign-three-unrestricted-free-agents|title=Lions sign three unrestricted free agents|website=www.detroitlions.com|language=en-US|access-date=March 14, 2019}}</ref>\n|5 years, $90 million<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nfl.com/news/story/0ap3000001021954/article/lions-expected-to-sign-trey-flowers-to-fiveyear-deal|title=Lions expected to sign Trey Flowers to five-year deal|website=NFL.com|language=en|access-date=March 12, 2019}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n|[[Placekicker|K]]\n|[[Stephen Gostkowski]]\n|New England Patriots\n|April 9, 2019<ref name=\":10\">{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/nfl/story/_/id/26481355|title=Source: Pats retain Gostkowski with 2-year deal|date=April 9, 2019|website=ESPN.com|language=en|access-date=April 10, 2019}}</ref>\n|2 years, $8.5 million<ref name=\":10\" />\n|-\n|[[Halfback (American football)|RB]]\n|[[Jeremy Hill]]\n|\n|\n|\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|WR\n|[[Chris Hogan (American football)|Chris Hogan]]\n|[[2019 Carolina Panthers season|Carolina Panthers]]\n|April 12, 2019<ref>{{cite web|title=Chris Hogan signs one-year contract with Panthers|url=https://www.panthers.com/news/chris-hogan-signs-one-year-contract-with-panthers|author=Strickland, Bryan|website=Panthers.com|date=April 12, 2019}}</ref>\n|1 year, $1.45 million<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.spotrac.com/nfl/carolina-panthers/chris-hogan-9068/|title=Chris Hogan|last=Spotrac.com|website=Spotrac.com|language=en-US|access-date=April 16, 2019}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|WR\n|[[Cody Hollister]]\n|[[2019 Tennessee Titans season|Tennessee Titans]]\n|May 13, 2019<ref>{{cite web|title=Titans Sign WR Cody Hollister|url=https://nfltraderumors.co/titans-sign-wr-cody-hollister/|author=Strickland, Bryan|website=nfltraderumors.co|date=May 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|2 years, $1.08 million<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.spotrac.com/nfl/tennessee-titans/cody-hollister-22299/|title=Cody Hollister|last=Spotrac.com|website=Spotrac.com|language=en-US|access-date=May 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Linebacker|LB]]\n|[[Ramon Humber]]\n|\n|\n|\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|OT\n|[[Ulrick John]]\n|New Orleans Saints\n|May 13, 2019<ref>{{cite web|title=Saints Announce Roster Moves Following Rookie Minicamp|url=https://www.neworleanssaints.com/news/saints-announce-roster-moves-following-rookie-minicamp|website=NewOrleansSaints.com|date=May 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|1 year, $720,000<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.spotrac.com/nfl/new-orleans-saints/ulrick-john-14643/|title=Ulrick John|last=Spotrac.com|website=Spotrac.com|language=en-US|access-date=May 20, 2019}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|LB\n|[[Albert McClellan]]\n|[[2019 New York Jets season|New York Jets]]\n|August 17, 2019<ref>{{cite web |last1=Wells |first1=MacGregor |title=Jets Sign LB Albert McClellan |url=https://www.ganggreennation.com/2019/8/17/20810523/jets-sign-lb-albert-mcclellan |website=ganggreennation.com |accessdate=August 18, 2019}}</ref>\n|1 year, $645,000<ref>{{cite web|url=https://overthecap.com/player/albert-mcclellan/1243/|title=Albert McClellan|website=OverTheCap.com|language=en-US|access-date=August 20, 2019}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n|[[Cornerback|CB]]\n|[[Jason McCourty]]\n|New England Patriots\n|March 14, 2019<ref name=\":5\">{{cite web|url=https://www.patriots.com/news/patriots-sign-rb-brandon-bolden-re-sign-cb-jason-mccourty|title=Patriots Sign RB Brandon Bolden; Re-Sign CB Jason McCourty|website=www.patriots.com|language=en-US|access-date=March 14, 2019}}</ref>\n|2 years, $10 million<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nesn.com/2019/03/jason-mccourty-receives-significant-pay-raise-with-new-patriots-contract/|title=Jason McCourty Receives Significant Pay Raise With New Patriots Contract|last=Cox|first=Zack|date=March 14, 2019|website=NESN.com|language=en|access-date=March 14, 2019}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\