ice-harris/ |website=profootballtalk.nbcsports.com |accessdate=August 25, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Keionta Davis: Waived/injured by Patriots|url=https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/football/news/keionta-davis-waivedinjured-by-patriots/|website=cbssports.com |accessdate=August 25, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|DE\n|[[Keionta Davis]]\n|New England Patriots<ref name=\"KeiontaDavisHarris\"/>\n|-\n|DT\n|[[Mike Pennel]]\n|[[2019 Kansas City Chiefs season|Kansas City Chiefs]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Goldma |first1=Charles |title=Report: Chiefs to sign DT Mike Pennel, release DT Terrell McClain |url=https://chiefswire.usatoday.com/2019/10/19/kansas-city-chiefs-sign-dt-mike-pennel-release-terrell-mclain-report/ |website=ChiefsWire.USAToday.com |publisher=USA Today |accessdate=October 20, 2019|date=October 19, 2019}}</ref>\n|rowspan=\"2\" | August 26, 2019<ref>{{cite web |title=Patriots Release DL Mike Pennel Jr. |url=https://www.patriots.com/news/patriots-release-dl-mike-pennel-jr |website=Patriots.com |accessdate=August 27, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Patriots release RB Robert Martin |url=https://www.patriots.com/news/patriots-release-rb-robert-martin |website=Patriots.com |accessdate=August 27, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Running back|RB]]\n|[[Robert Martin (American football)|Robert Martin]]\n|\n|-\n|WR\n|Maurice Harris\n|\n|August 27, 2019<ref>{{cite web |last1=Hannable |first1=Ryan |title=Patriots WR Maurice Harris released from IR with injury settlement |url=https://weei.radio.com/blogs/ryan-hannable/patriots-roster-move-maurice-harris-becomes-free-agent |website=WEEI.Radio.com |accessdate=August 31, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|TE\n|[[Andrew Beck (American football)|Andrew Beck]]\n|[[2019 Denver Broncos season|Denver Broncos]]<ref name=\"waiverclaims2k19\" />\n|rowspan=\"10\" | August 30, 2019<ref>{{cite web |last1=Buchmasser |first1=Bernd |title=2019 Patriots roster cuts tracker: rumors, news, instant analysis and more |url=https://www.patspulpit.com/2019/8/30/20838109/2019-nfl-ros