m, the Patriots were granted an additional 91st spot which was allocated to German [[Fullback (gridiron football)|fullback]] [[Jakob Johnson]].\n\n{| class=\"toccolours\" style=\"text-align: left;\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"9\" style=\"background-color: #0C2340; color: #FFFFFF; text-align: center; border:2px solid #C8102E;\"| New England Patriots 2019 opening training camp roster\n|-\n| style=\"font-size: 95%;\" valign=\"top\" | '''Quarterbacks'''\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">12</span> [[Tom Brady]]\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">5</span> [[Danny Etling]]\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">2</span> [[Brian Hoyer]]\n*''<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">58</span> [[Jarrett Stidham]]''\n'''Running backs'''\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">38</span> [[Brandon Bolden]]\n*''<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">64</span> [[Nick Brossette]]''\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">34</span> [[Rex Burkhead]]\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">46</span> [[James Develin]] FB\n*''<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">53</span> [[Damien Harris]]''\n*''<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">47</span> [[Jakob Johnson]]'' FB\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">26</span> [[Sony Michel]]\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">28</span> [[James White (running back)|James White]]\n\n'''Wide receivers'''\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">14</span> [[Braxton Berrios]]\n*''<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">65</span> [[Ryan Davis (wide receiver)|Ryan Davis]]''\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">13</span> [[Phillip Dorsett]]\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">11</span> [[Julian Edelman]]\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">82</span> [[Maurice Harris (American football)|Maurice Harris]]\n*''<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">50</span> [[N'Keal Harry]]''\n*<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">15</span> [[Dontrelle Inman]] \n*''<span style=\"font-family: