98/ |website=Spotrac.com |publisher=Spotrac |accessdate=October 28, 2019|date=October 28, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|QB\n|Cody Kessler\n|New England Patriots\n|October 28, 2019<ref name=\"KesSlerReSignsOctober\">{{cite web |last1=Alper |first1=Josh |title=Patriots bring back Cody Kessler |url=https://profootballtalk.nbcsports.com/2019/10/28/patriots-bring-back-cody-kessler/ |website=ProFootballTalk.NBCSports.com |publisher=NBC Sports |accessdate=October 28, 2019|date=October 28, 2019}}</ref>\n|1 year, $720,000<ref>{{cite web |title=Cody Kessler|url=https://www.spotrac.com/nfl/new-england-patriots/cody-kessler-19046/|website=Spotrac.com |accessdate=November 8, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|K\n|[[Nick Folk]]\n|Arizona Hotshots (AAF)\n|October 29, 2019<ref name=\"FolKNic\" />\n|1 year, $1.03 million<ref>{{cite web |title=Nick Folk |url=https://www.spotrac.com/nfl/tampa-bay-buccaneers/nick-folk-2418/ |website=Spotrac.com |publisher=Spotrac |accessdate=November 8, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|K\n|[[Kai Forbath]]\n|Jacksonville Jaguars\n|November 29, 2019<ref>{{cite web|title=Patriots sign K Kai Forbath; Release K Nick Folk|url=https://www.patriots.com/news/patriots-sign-k-kai-forbath-release-k-nick-folk|date=November 29, 2019}}</ref> \n|1 year, $930,000<ref>{{cite web |title=Kai Forbath |url=https://www.spotrac.com/nfl/dallas-cowboys/kai-forbath-8857/ |website=Spotrac.com |publisher=Spotrac |accessdate=December 22, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|DT\n|[[Albert Huggins]]\n|Philadelphia Eagles\n|December 2, 2019<ref name=\"HugginsForbath\">{{cite web|title=Patriots claim DL Albert Huggins from Philadelphia; Release K Kai Forbath|url=https://www.patriots.com/news/patriots-claim-dl-albert-huggins-from-philadelphia-release-k-kai-forbath|website=Patriots.com|date=December 2, 2019}}</ref>\n|1 year, $1.08 million<ref>{{cite web |title=Albert Huggins |url=https://www.google.com/search?safe=active&q=albert+huggins+contract&rlz=1CAQIMT_enUS879&oq=albert+huggins+contract&aqs=chrome.0.0j69i57.4833j1j4&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-